<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَتَصْرِيفِ الرِّيَاحِ}</span> ... تَقْلِيبِهَا فيِ مَهَابِّهَا لِمَنْفَعَتِكُمْ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
