<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَفَّاكٍ}</span> ... كَذَّابٍ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَثِيمٍ}</span> ... كَثِيرِ الإِثْمِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{هُزُوًا}</span> ... سُخْرِيَةً.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(١٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْفُلْكُ}</span> ... السُّفُنُ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(١٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لا يَرْجُون أَيَّامَ اللَّهِ}</span> ... لَا يَتَوَقَّعُونَ وَقَائِعَهُ وَعَذَابَهُ بِأَعْدَائِهِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(١٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْكِتَابَ}</span> ... التَّوْرَاةَ، وَالإِنْجِيلَ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(١٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَالْحُكْمَ}</span> ... تَحْكِيمَهُمَا.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(١٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بَيِّنَاتٍ مِّنَ الْأَمْرِ}</span> ... شَرَائِعَ وَاضِحَاتٍ فيِ الحَلَالِ، وَالحَرَامِ، وَدَلَالَاتٍ تُبَيِّنُ الحَقَّ مِنَ البَاطِلِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(١٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بَغْيًا بَيْنَهُمْ}</span> ... حَسَدًا وَعَدَاوَةً بَيْنَهُمْ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(١٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{شَرِيعَةٍ مِّنَ الْأَمْرِ}</span> ... مِنْهَاجٍ وَاضِحٍ مِنْ أَمْرِ الدِّينِ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
